description: The image shows a presentation on "Customer Segmentation" taking place in a large hall. A large screen displays a diagram, which is a circle divided into three segments labeled "Precision," "Rationale," and "Ambiguity," connected by lines in the center. In front of the screen, a man stands near the center of the stage, seemingly observing the presentation. Seated in the foreground on the left is a woman holding a cup. The hall is illuminated with blue and purple lighting. The floor is covered with a patterned carpet. There are curtains in the background and some lights on the stage.
